Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我和乌尔曼先生有预约\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi. I've got an appointment with Mr. Ullman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我叫杰克·托伦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My name is Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的办公室是左手边第一间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His office is the first door on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,-乌尔曼先生  -正是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mr. Ullman? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我是杰克·托伦斯  -快请进  杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm Jack Torrance. - Oh, come on in, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴认识你  乌尔曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to meet you too, Mr. Ullman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这是我的秘书  苏希  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is my secretary, Susie. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,-苏希  你好  -我们这里难找吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Susie, how do you do? - Any trouble finding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:54.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,一点不难找  我三个半小时就到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem at all. I made the trip in 3 and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,那真是算很快了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's very good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,快请坐吧  杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit down a minute, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,在这千万别拘束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,要来杯咖啡吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有的话  就来点吧  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're having some, I wouldn't mind. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-苏希  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Susie. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,去叫比尔·沃森来跟我们一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And would you ask Bill Watson to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我这就去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想去住在那个酒店里过冬天吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you really want to go and live in that hotel for the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll be lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  应该是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:39.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,反正  这里也没什么人一起玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, there's hardly anybody to play with around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:45.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  结交新朋友总是需要花些时间的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know. It always takes a little time to make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  或许是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他肯定很期待去酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's looking forward to the hotel, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我才不呢  托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I ain't, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  托尼  别犯傻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, come on, Tony. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想去那里  托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to go there, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不想去呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How come you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不想去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就走着瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都会玩得很开心的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're all going to have a real good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔  我想介绍你认识一下杰克·托伦斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill, I'd like you to meet Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你好  比尔  -你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How do you do, Bill? - How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你  -很高兴认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Nice to meet you. - Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧  比尔  一起聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grab a chair, Bill. Join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克今年冬天会帮我们照看眺望酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack is going to take care of the Overlook for us this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,等我们谈完  希望你带他四处转转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd like you to take him around place soon as we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克是学校里的老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack is a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,以前是老师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, formerly a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在做什么工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What line of work are you in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是个作家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:42.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,教书差不多就是为了糊口而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Teaching's been more or less a way of making ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,如今这样对你来说应该是个很大的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This ought to be quite a change for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待有变化\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm looking for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在丹佛的人强烈推荐杰克  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our people in Denver recommended Jack very highly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我同意他们说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚说到哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's see, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚  准备给你解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was ,yeah, about to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的营业季是从5月15号到10月30号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that our season here runs from may 15th to October 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后彻底停业  到第二年的5月再开业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then we close down completely until the following May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能问问为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you mind if I ask why you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来在这里滑雪应该会很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It seems to me that the skiing up here would be fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,的确是的  问题在于要花费巨大的成本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would be. The problem is the enormous cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,维持到萨德温德镇的路面能够通行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it would be to keep the road to Sidewinder open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是段25英里的路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a 25-mile stretch of road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,冬天的降雪厚度能有20英尺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It gets 20 feet of snow during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:28.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,要保持路面畅通  从经济上来看是完全不划算的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's just no way to make it economically feasible to keep it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,1907年建这个地方的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When the place was built in 1907...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们对冬季运动尚不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there was very little interest in winter sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:39.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,选择这里完全是看中其幽静的环境和美丽的风景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This site was chosen for its seclusion and scenic beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里的确够幽静和美丽的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's certainly got plenty of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,在丹佛时  他们有没有告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did they give you any idea in Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,这份工作具体是做什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about what the job entails?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,就大致说了一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only in a very general way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,冬季真的会无比残酷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The winters can be fantastically cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,基本就是要应对高额的损坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The basic idea is to cope with the very costly damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及可能出现的折旧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and depreciation which can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,这主要包括烧锅炉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This consists mainly of running the boiler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,每天例行给酒店的不同区域供暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}heating different parts of the hotel on a daily rotating basis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,出现损坏及时修理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}repairing damage as it occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,及时修理小毛病就不会变成大问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and doing repairs so the elements can't get a foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That sounds fine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,从体力上说  这份工作要求不高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Physically, it's not a very demanding job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,在冬天  唯一一件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only thing that can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,可能会有点难熬的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get a bit trying here during the winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是会有强烈的孤独感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is a tremendous sense of isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,那恰恰就是我想寻求的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that just happens to be exactly what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正在写新作品的大纲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm outlining a new writing project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:40.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,五个月宁静的时光正是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, five months of peace is just what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,那很好  杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's very good, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为  对有的人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because, for some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,孤独  与世隔绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}solitude ...and isolation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,本身  就会成为问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can, of itself, become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你夫人和儿子呢  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about your wife and son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他们能接受吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think they'll take to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们会很喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我把你交接给比尔之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, before I turn you over to Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:14.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还有一件事我们需要聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there's one other thing I think we should talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想耸人听闻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to sound melodramatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是这件事的确会让有些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's something been known to give a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,犹豫到底要不要接受这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}second thoughts about the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很有兴趣知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得在丹佛时他们应该没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't suppose they tell you anything in Denver
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,1970年冬天发生在这里的一起悲剧事件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the tragedy we had up here during the winter of 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们似乎的确没说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't believe they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这个职位的前任负责人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My predecessor in this job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,雇了一个叫查尔斯·格拉迪的人当冬季管理员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}hired a man named Charles Grady as the winter caretaker.
