Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,相当离奇的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}quite a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  的确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还是很难相信这事真的是在这里发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's still hard for me to believe it actually happened here.
