Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:25.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信等我告诉她  她会被深深地吸引住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure she'll be absolutely fascinated when I tell her.
