Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  这地方很美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你和丹尼肯定会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You and Danny are going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼  你为什么不想去那家酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony, why don't you want to go to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定知道  快点告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You do too know. Now come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜托啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼  告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Tony, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在把眼睛睁开让我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, hold your eyes still so I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好  另一只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's good. Now the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你记不记得在刷牙的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when you were brushing your teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,闻到什么奇怪的气味\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}do you remember if you smelled anything funny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者看到什么强烈的闪光  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or saw any bright, flashing lights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是任何奇怪的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or anything at all strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得你之前在刷牙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember when you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,刷牙之后紧接着发生的事  你还记得什么  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the next thing you remember after you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:03.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈在说  "醒醒  醒醒  丹尼  醒醒"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mom was saying, "Wake up. Wake up, Danny, wake up. "
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:08.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼  你还记不记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Danny, can you remember what you were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,在开始刷牙之前你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just before you started brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,和托尼说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是你的宠物吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is Tony one of your animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  他是住在我嘴里的小男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. He's a little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是他的幻想好友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony's his imaginary friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在能不能张开嘴  让我见见托尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you were to open your mouth now, could I see Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为他藏起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because he hides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where does he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,进我肚子里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼让你做过什么事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does Tony ever tell you to do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再聊托尼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to talk about Tony anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:57.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想请你帮我个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to ask you to do me a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:10.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天都乖乖地躺在床上  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and stay quietly in bed for the rest of the day. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,一定要这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我希望你听话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. I'd like you to.
