Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:43.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫人  我觉得你无需担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, I don't think you have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:47.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我非常肯定丹尼的身体没有任何问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm quite sure there's nothing physically wrong with Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,他现在看上去没有任何问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He seems absolutely fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你真该看看他之前的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you should've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,小孩出点事能把做父母的吓死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kids can scare you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我  这种突然的发作一点也不罕见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But believe me, these episodes are not at all uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然看起来很糟  但实际情况并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And they look much worse than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过他到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But what was the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫人  很多时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, Most of the time,
