Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不了  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在博尔德待了很久吗  托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you been in Boulder long, Mrs. Torrance?
