Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼的初次出现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Tony's first appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,是否恰好是你们搬来这里的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}happen to coincide with your arrival here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想丹尼开始跟托尼说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess Danny started talking to Tony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,大约是在我们送他进幼儿园的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the time we put him in nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对于学校生活适应得好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did he adjust well to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,起先他不太喜欢上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't like it too much at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后他受了伤  所以我们有阵子没让他去上学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then he had an injury, so we kept him out for a while and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  差不多就是那时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I guess that's about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我发现他在跟托尼说话的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I first noticed he was talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,他受了什么伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What sort of injury did he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的肩膀脱臼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He dislocated his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么弄的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did he manage to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是小孩子常见的那种情况  你懂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was just one of those things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,纯粹是意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Purely an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫一直在酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My husband had been drinking and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,他那天晚回来三个多小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he came home about three hours late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那晚他心情不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So he wasn't exactly in the greatest mood that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:59.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼把书本和作业纸弄得满屋子都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Danny had scattered some of his school papers all over the room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫抓住他的胳膊  把他拉开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and my husband grabbed his arm to pull him away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是父母常会对小孩做的那种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just the sort of thing you do 100 times with a child
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,在公园里  或街上  都很常见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, in a park or in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But on this particular occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫用力过猛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my husband just used too much strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,伤到了丹尼的胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he injured Danny's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过  这事还是有些好处的 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, something good did come out of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because he said:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,"温蒂  我再也不会喝一滴酒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Wendy, I'm never going to touch another drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我再喝  你就离开我"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if I do, you can leave me. "
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后他就再没喝过酒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,他五个月没有沾酒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hasn't had any alcohol in 5 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:42.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,152)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs30\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HFFFFFF&}停  业  日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定在很高的地方  空气都感觉很不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We must really be high up. The air feels so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你应该吃早餐的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should've eaten your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,等到了酒店我就给你弄东西吃  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll get you something as soon as we get to the hotel. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,唐纳大队不就是在这里被雪困住的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wasn't it around here that the Donner party got snowbound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:41.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该是更靠西的地方  在内华达山脉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think that was farther west, in the Sierras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么是唐纳大队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was the Donner party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:51.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,是西部大开发时期的一群移民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were a party of settlers in covered wagon times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,有年冬天  他们被大雪困在了大山里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They got snowbound one winter in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了活命  他们不得不靠吃人肉为生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They had to resort to cannibalism in order to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是说他们把自己人给吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean they ate each other up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样才能生存下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They had to in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:13.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道关于食人的事  我在电视上看过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know all about cannibalism. I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞧吧  没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在电视上看过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He saw it on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,-飞机什么时候起飞  -8点半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What time does the plane leave? - 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们还有足够的时间把各项事宜再过一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That gives us plenty of time to go over everything first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,-再见  乌尔曼先生  -再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  杰克  希望没让你等太久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, Jack. I hope you haven't been waiting too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  刚好让我们有时间吃点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem. In fact we had time to grab a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  很高兴你们在厨房关停前赶到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good. Glad you made it before they shut down the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你好  -你的家人到处看过了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi. - Is your family having a look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我儿子发现了游戏室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, my son's discovered the games room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,-行李都拿进来了吧  -就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Has your luggage been brought in? - Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于我们今天要带你了解不少地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In view of all the ground we have to cover today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我建议我们先快速看一下你们的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suggest we have a quick look at your apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后立刻开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and get started straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,比尔  你能安排先把托伦斯一家的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill, would you have the Torrances' things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,送到他们的公寓去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}brought to their apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好的  -我最好先叫一下我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Fine. - I'd better collect my family first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:38.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的科罗拉多休闲室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is our Colorado Lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里真是美极了  不是吗  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This place is fantastic, isn't it, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过这样的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些印第安风格的设计都是真品吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are all these Indian designs authentic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:59.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,好像主要是根据纳瓦霍族和阿帕切族的图案设计的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe they're based mainly on Navajo and Apache motifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的太美了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're really gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:01.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,实际上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As a matter of fact
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是我见过的最美的酒店了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this is probably the most gorgeous hotel I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,这家老酒店有着辉煌的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This old place has had an illustrious past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,在其全盛时期  曾住满了社会名流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In its heyday, it was one of the stopping place for the jet setters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,即便那时大家都还不知道社会名流是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even before anybody knew what a jet set was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,有四位总统曾在此住过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had four presidents who stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,很多电影明星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lots of movie stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,有皇室的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:23.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,都是最上层的人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the best people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是酒店的员工宿舍侧楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the staff wing of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:23.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,其它卧室冬天都不供暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}None of the other bedrooms are heated during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,-再见  乌尔曼先生  -再见  姑娘们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Goodbye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你们的住处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And here are your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,起居室  卧室  洗手间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Living room, bedroom, bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有给你们的儿子住的小房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a small bedroom for your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常适合小孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perfect for a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  这房子独门独户  不用跟别人共用设施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then. Place is very nicely self-contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,也好打理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Easy to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  非常适合一家人居住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, very cozy for a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们想换个环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you feel like spreading out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:03.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,酒店的其他地方也随便你们住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you have the rest of the hotel to move around in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:07.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里真是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:09.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,太有家的感觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}homey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们著名的树篱迷宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is our famous hedge maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:19.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,算是这里的一处独特景点吧  墙有13英尺高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's quite an attraction here. The walls are 13 feet high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,树篱和酒店一样历史悠久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the hedge is as old as the hotel itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:23.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我一般是不会进去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wouldn't want to go in there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非我有一小时的空闲时间用来找出路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}unless I had an hour to spare to find my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,眺望酒店是什么时候建成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When was the Overlook built?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,1907年开始建造\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Construction started in 1907.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,1909年完工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was finished in 1909.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经是一座印第安坟场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The site's supposed to be on an Indian burial ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  他们在施工时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I believe they actually had to repel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,不得不打退几次印第安人的袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a few Indian attacks as they were building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:47.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的雪地车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's our Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们都会开车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you both drive a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:51.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:54.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为驾驶雪地车基本和开车一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because basically the Snowcat operates very much like a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能掌握诀窍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It won't take you long to get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:23:58.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As a matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:02.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去年从芝加哥请了一位设计师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we brought a decorator in from Chicago just last year
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,给酒店的这一部分进行重新装修\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to refurbish this part of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:07.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,他确实装修得很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He sure did a beautiful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,粉色和金色是我最喜欢的颜色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pink and gold are my favorite colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:12.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的金色舞厅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, this is our Gold Ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:15.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就说嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以轻松容纳三百人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can accommodate up to 300 people here very comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  我们可以在这里办一场盛大的派对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy, I bet you we could really have a good party in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你们办不起来多么盛大的派对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid you won't do too well here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们能自带物资\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}unless you brought supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们停业时  会将酒全部撤走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We always remove the booze from the premises when we shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:33.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,那可以减少我们通常得承担的保险费用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That reduces the insurance we normally have to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:35.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:36.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你们走运了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:41.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪克  快过来跟托伦斯夫妇打个招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, come on over and say hello to Mr. and Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.06,0:24:43.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,这位是迪克·哈洛兰  我们的主厨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Dick Hallorann, our head chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.29,0:24:45.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,-哈洛兰先生  我是杰克  -很高兴认识你  杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mr. Hallorann, I'm Jack. - Glad to meet you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:46.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,这位是我妻子  温妮芙德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my wife, Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:47.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你  温妮芙德  -很高兴认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Glad to meet you, Winifred. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:50.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫妇今年冬天会替我们照料眺望酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Torrances are gonna take care of the Overlook for us this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.18,0:24:55.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  你们目前觉得这个酒店怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's just great. How do you folks like our hotel so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.02,0:24:56.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,简直棒极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.79,0:24:57.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我发现他在外面找你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found him outside looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:05.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,丹  你厌倦轰炸宇宙了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dan, did you get tired of bombing the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:06.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:08.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:10.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -谢谢你  苏希\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thanks. - Thank you, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.45,0:25:12.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪克  如果你准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, if you're ready to do it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以带托伦斯夫人去看看厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it'd be a good idea if you could show Mrs. Torrance the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.85,0:25:16.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我再继续跟杰克交代交代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}while I continue on with Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:19.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常乐意  这边请  托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would be a pleasure. Right this way, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:21.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  待会儿见  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great. See you later, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,回见  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.19,0:25:26.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(115.5,44)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HB8B8E7&}安全出口  不得堵塞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:28.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫人  你丈夫介绍你时  叫你温妮芙德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, your husband introduced you as Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:30.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我应该叫你温妮还是芙莱蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, are you a "Winnie," or a "Freddie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.13,0:25:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,叫我温蒂就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.64,0:25:35.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,温蒂啊  真好听  再好听不过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Wendy. That's nice. That's the prettiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.00,0:25:37.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  这厨房太气派了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God, this is the kitchen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:25:39.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  正是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.57,0:25:42.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  丹尼  够大吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you like it, Danny? Is it big enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.17,0:25:45.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这是我见过的最大的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's the biggest place I ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  这里简直就是一个巨大的迷宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, this whole place is such an enormous maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:49.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得每次进来这儿 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like I'll have to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.30,0:25:51.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,都得撒面包屑  标记返回的路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}leave a trail of breadcrumbs every time I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.81,0:25:54.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,别灰心  托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't let it get you down, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是很大  但也不过是个厨房而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's big, but it still ain't nothing but a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:25:59.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,而且这里的很多东西你连碰都不用碰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a lot of this stuff you'll never have to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:02.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算真让我碰  我也不知道怎么用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't know what to do with it if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.40,0:26:05.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少你们丝毫不用担心食物的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, one thing for sure, you don't have to worry about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:08.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们一家可以在这里吃上一整年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because ou folks could eat up here a whole year
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.75,0:26:10.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,菜单都不带重样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and never have the same menu twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的步入式冷冻室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, right here is our walk-in freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.11,0:26:17.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们将所有肉类都储存在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this is where we keep all of our meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.18,0:26:20.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,15扇肋排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got 15 rib roasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:22.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,30袋汉堡肉  每袋重10磅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}30 ten-pound bags of hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.73,0:26:26.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,12只火鸡  大概40只鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got 12 turkeys, about 40 chickens...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.03,0:26:29.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,50块西冷牛排  24卷猪排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}50 sirloin steaks, two dozen of pork roast...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.39,0:26:32.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有20只羊腿  你喜欢羊肉吗  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 20 legs of lamb. Do you like lamb, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不喜欢  -不喜欢吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你最喜欢吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, what's your favorite food, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.07,0:26:37.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,炸薯条配番茄酱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}French fries and ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,那也没问题  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I think we can manage that too, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.95,0:26:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来  小心脚下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come along, now. Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:47.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛兰先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.28,0:26:51.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我们叫他博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how'd you know we call him Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.11,0:26:51.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.14,0:26:55.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,「博士」  你刚才两次那样叫丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doc. You called Danny "Doc" twice just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I did? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.50,0:26:58.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有时候叫他博士 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We call him Doc sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:00.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像兔八哥卡通片里的博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like in the Bugs Bunny cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.87,0:27:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你是怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.37,0:27:05.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想可能是因为我听见你那样叫过他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I guess I probably heard you call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:07.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,有可能  但我真不记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's possible. But I honestly don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.53,0:27:09.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们见面之后  我那样叫过他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}calling him that since we've been with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.98,0:27:12.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来就像个博士  对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, anyway, he looks like a Doc, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.67,0:27:14.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,「还好吗  博士」\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's up, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:19.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  这里是储藏室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this is the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.80,0:27:22.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫人  在这里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In here, Mrs. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:25.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,存放着我们所有的干货和罐头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is where we keep all the dried goods and the canned goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.89,0:27:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,有水果罐头  蔬菜罐头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got canned fruits and vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.47,0:27:32.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,鱼罐头  肉罐头  各种冷吃热吃麦片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}canned fish and meats, hot and cold cereals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:35.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,博斯特麦片  玉米片  膨化甜麦片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Post Toasties, Corn Flakes, Sugar Puffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.81,0:27:40.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,脆米麦片  燕麦片  脆小麦麦片  还有麦乳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rice Krispies, oatmeal, Wheatena and Cream of Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.10,0:27:42.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,几十罐黑糖蜜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got a dozen jugs of black molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.71,0:27:45.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,60盒奶粉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got 60 boxes of dried milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:55.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想吃冰激凌吗  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How'd you like some ice cream, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.61,0:28:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,饼干  手指卷面包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sociables, finger rolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.61,0:28:02.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有七种其他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 7 kinds of what have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.39,0:28:06.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,有桃干  杏干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, we've got dried peaches, dried apricots...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.19,0:28:08.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,葡萄干还有西梅干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dried raisins and dried prunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:10.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,托伦斯夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Mrs. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:13.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,想过得快乐  就得保持日常生活细节不变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you got to keep regular if you want to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.70,0:28:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,-参观得怎么样  -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How're you getting on? - Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.55,0:28:20.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,迪克  能让托伦斯夫人跟我们来一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, can we borrow Mrs. Torrance for a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.92,0:28:22.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们正要去地下室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're on our way through to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我保证不会很久的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise we won't keep her very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:27.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  乌尔曼先生  我们正要去吃冰激凌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem, Mr. Ullman. I was just getting to the ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:30.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你喜欢冰激凌吧  博士  -喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You like ice cream, Doc? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:31.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.76,0:28:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You folks don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我带丹尼吃点冰激凌  边吃边等你们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I give Danny some ice cream while we waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.96,0:28:37.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,-当然不  -不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not at all. - No, we don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.04,0:28:38.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好  -你觉得好不好  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good. - Sound good to you, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:41.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好  -好  你要乖乖的哦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Okay, you behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:46.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢什么冰激凌  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind of ice cream do you like, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.59,0:28:47.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:50.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就吃巧克力口味的  来吧  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chocolate it shall be. Come on, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天大家似乎都很忙乱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing, how much activities going on today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.40,0:28:59.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  昨天客人们还有一些员工离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Well, the guests and some of the staff left yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.73,0:29:01.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,但停业前最后一天总是很忙乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the last day's always hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.86,0:29:05.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,大家都想尽早上路离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody wants to be on their way as early as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.27,0:29:09.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,等到今晚5点  就像没人在这里存在过一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By 5 o'clock tonight, you'll never know anybody was ever here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:12.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,-就像一艘幽灵船  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just like a ghost ship, huh? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.39,0:29:20.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我是怎么知道你叫"博士"的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know how I knew your name was Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.86,0:29:29.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在说什么  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what I'm talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:39.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我记得  我小时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can remember when I was a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:42.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我奶奶和我全程不张嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my grandmother and I could hold conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,就可以进行对话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}entirely without ever opening our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.73,0:29:49.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,她称之为「闪灵」能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She called it "Shining."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.67,0:29:53.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,很久以来  我以为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And for a long time I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:56.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们祖孙俩有这种能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was just the two of us that had "the Shine" to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:30:00.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像你可能以为只有你一个人有一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like you probably thought you was the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.31,0:30:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,但其实还有别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there are other folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.44,0:30:06.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他们自己不知道  或者不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though mostly they don't know it, or don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.81,0:30:13.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你从什么时候开始有这能力的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long have you been able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:21.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不想说呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.09,0:30:28.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.71,0:30:32.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁说你不应该说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who says you ain't supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:37.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.05,0:30:41.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:47.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼是住在我嘴里的小男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony's the little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.60,0:30:53.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,是托尼告诉你一些事的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is Tony the one that tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.96,0:30:59.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是怎么告诉你那些事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How does he tell you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.15,0:31:06.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我睡着以后  他给我看一些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's like I go to sleep, and he shows me things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.64,0:31:10.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,但等我醒来  我什么都记不得了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But when I wake up, I can't remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:16.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,你爸妈知道托尼的存在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does your mom and dad know about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.56,0:31:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.62,0:31:21.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道他会告诉你一些事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do they know he tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:25.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼告诉我  千万别告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony told me never to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.13,0:31:31.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,托尼跟你说过关于这里的一些事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has Tony ever told you anything about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.69,0:31:34.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,关于眺望酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About the Overlook Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.56,0:31:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想  博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now think real hard, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.62,0:31:43.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,想想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:49.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许他给我看过一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe he showed me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.71,0:31:53.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,努力想想是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Try to think of what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.37,0:31:59.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛兰先生  你怕这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann, are you scared of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我才不怕这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Scared of nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.49,0:32:06.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,只不过...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.73,0:32:10.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,有些地方就跟人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, some places are like people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.38,0:32:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,有些有闪灵能力  有些没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some shine and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.95,0:32:18.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以说眺望酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess you could say the Overlook Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.00,0:32:21.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,就有类似于闪灵的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has something about it that's like shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:26.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里有不好的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there something bad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.79,0:32:41.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,其实  博士  当某件事发生之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Doc, when something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.42,0:32:44.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,它会在身后留下踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it can leave a trace of itself behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.92,0:32:47.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,就比如说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.64,0:32:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人烤焦了吐司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if someone burns toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.83,0:32:57.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许某些事发生后会留下其他类型的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe things that happen leave other kind of traces behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.64,0:33:01.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是人人都能注意得到的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not things that anyone can notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:07.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有拥有闪灵能力的人才能看到的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But things that people who shine can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.16,0:33:11.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,就像他们能看见尚未发生的事情一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like they can see things that haven't happened yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.80,0:33:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,有时他们也能看见很久以前发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sometimes they can see things that happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.40,0:33:22.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得就这家酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think a lot of things happened right here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:26.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,多年来肯定发生过很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in this particular hotel over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.76,0:33:29.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,并不全是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And not all of them was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.45,0:33:34.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,237号房是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.49,0:33:40.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,237号房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.96,0:33:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕237号房  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're scared of room 237, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.77,0:33:48.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.76,0:33:53.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛兰先生  237号房里有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann, what is in room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.03,0:33:56.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,237号房里什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There ain't nothing in room 237.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.21,0:34:03.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,但反正你也不需要进去做什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you ain't got no business going in there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.72,0:34:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以别进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.96,0:34:08.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗  别进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You understand? Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.54,0:34:13.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,152)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑_GBK\fs30\b0\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HFFFFFF&}一个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,早  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:53.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的早餐好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,几点了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:57.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,大概11点半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's about 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.24,0:36:01.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,11点半  老天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eleven-thirty, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:04.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们熬夜熬得太晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess we've been staying up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.04,0:36:06.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.89,0:36:10.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我按你的喜好煎了蛋  只煎一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I made them just the way you like them, sunny-side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.38,0:36:12.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,真棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.85,0:36:16.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,外面很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's really pretty outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.87,0:36:19.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,你吃完早餐之后  带我出去散散步怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about taking me for a walk after you finish your breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:24.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该先试着写点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suppose I ought to try to do some writing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:27.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,有灵感了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any ideas yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.15,0:36:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,思如泉涌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lots of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.07,0:36:32.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,可惜都算不上好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.06,0:36:35.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会想到好点子的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, something will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.89,0:36:39.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,关键是你得适应每天都写作的习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just a matter of settling into the habit of writing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.53,0:36:42.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  那就是关键\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep. That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.28,0:36:47.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里真的很好  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's really nice up here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.01,0:36:49.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爱这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.01,0:36:51.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的很爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没这么开心自在过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never been this happy or comfortable anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.06,0:36:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这么快就适应了这大房子  真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing how fast you get used to such a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.61,0:37:02.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  我们刚来的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I tell you, when we first came up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.64,0:37:04.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还觉得这里有点吓人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought it was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:07.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我立马就爱上了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fell in love with it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.48,0:37:11.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我过来面试的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I came up here for my interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.70,0:37:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像以前来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was as though I'd been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.70,0:37:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都有过似曾相识的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, we all have moments of déjà vu,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.55,0:37:20.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这也太离奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but this was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.47,0:37:23.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was almost as though I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.73,0:37:26.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,每个角落会有什么一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what was going to be around every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.52,0:38:03.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,输的人要打扫全美国  怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The loser has to keep America clean. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.80,0:38:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,-好啊  -你输定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right. - And you're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.58,0:38:09.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要抓到你了  你最好跑快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm going to get you. You'd better run fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:15.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:18.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要追上来了  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm coming in close. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.13,0:38:20.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,输的人要把美国打扫干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Loser has to keep America clean.
