Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.90,1:05:23.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你给我倒一杯  我就喝光一杯  劳埃德  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You set them up and I'll knock them back, Lloyd,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.23,1:05:24.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,一杯接一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.40,1:05:29.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,白人的负担  劳埃德  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}White man's burden, Lloyd, my man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.57,1:05:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,白人的负担\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}White man's burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.86,1:05:38.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.83,1:05:41.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时囊中羞涩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it seems I'm temporarily light.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.17,1:05:44.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里的信用怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's my credit in this joint, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.89,1:05:46.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,您的信用没问题  托伦斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your credit's fine, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.06,1:05:49.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.86,1:05:51.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like you, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.65,1:05:53.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I always liked you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.62,1:05:55.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一直是最优秀的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were always the best of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.07,1:06:01.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,从廷巴克图到缅因州的波特兰  最优秀的酒保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Best goddamned bartender from Timbuktu to Portland, Maine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.88,1:06:04.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者是俄勒冈州的波特兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or Portland, Oregon, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.44,1:06:05.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you for saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.42,1:06:12.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,敬我戒酒的这悲惨的五个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here's to five miserable months on the wagon
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.24,1:06:16.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及它给我造成的无法弥补的伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and all the irreparable harm that it's caused me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.48,1:06:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,您过得还好吗  托伦斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are things going, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.40,1:06:41.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是很好  劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things could be better, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.29,1:06:45.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,非常不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things could be a whole lot better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.10,1:06:48.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我希望不是什么大事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.58,1:06:50.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.31,1:06:53.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是大事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.81,1:07:01.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过是跟楼上那个"精子银行"发生了点口角\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just a little problem with the old sperm bank upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.11,1:07:04.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,不过我都能应付  劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing I can't handle, though, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.78,1:07:05.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.92,1:07:07.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,女人啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Women.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.02,1:07:09.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,受不了她们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't live with them
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.80,1:07:11.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,却又少不了她们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can't live without them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.93,1:07:16.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,至理名言  劳埃德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Words of wisdom, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.54,1:07:19.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,至理名言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.32,1:07:33.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没打过他  该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never laid a hand on him, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.80,1:07:35.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.34,1:07:42.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我都舍不得碰他那小脑袋上的一根头发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't touch one hair on his goddamn little head.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.61,1:07:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爱那个小混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love the little son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.38,1:07:50.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意为他做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.33,1:07:53.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈是任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any fucking thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.47,1:08:00.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那个贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.73,1:08:03.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要我还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.90,1:08:06.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,她就不会让我忘记以前的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she'll never let me forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.76,1:08:19.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我确实伤过他一次  行了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did hurt him once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.03,1:08:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是个意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.45,1:08:24.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我完全是无意的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Completely unintentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.28,1:08:28.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,那可能发生在任何人身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It could have happened to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.28,1:08:33.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,那已经是他妈三年前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it was three goddamn years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.92,1:08:36.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个小鬼把我的稿子丢得满地都是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The little fucker had thrown all my papers all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.69,1:08:38.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想把他拉起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I tried to do was pull him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.12,1:08:46.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍微丧失了一下肌肉协调能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A momentary loss of muscular coordination.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.16,1:08:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是指...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.84,1:08:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,多用了那么一点点力气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few extra foot-pounds of energy...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.49,1:08:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,就那一秒  那一秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}per second, per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.09,1:09:01.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.89,1:09:11.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.59,1:09:13.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.42,1:09:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.72,1:09:18.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,酒店里除了我们还有其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's someone else in the hotel with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.12,1:09:21.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,某间房里有个疯女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a crazy woman in one of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.99,1:09:23.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,她想勒死丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She tried to strangle Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.91,1:09:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you out of your fucking mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.71,1:09:30.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.32,1:09:32.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the truth! Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.96,1:09:35.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓  是丹尼告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear it. Danny told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.87,1:09:37.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,他跑到某间卧室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He went up into one of the bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.95,1:09:41.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,房门开着  他看到浴缸里有个疯女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The door was open, and he saw this crazy woman in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.67,1:09:43.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,她想勒死他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She tried to strangle him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.63,1:09:49.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,是哪间房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which room was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.26,1:09:59.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密十频道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From Channel 10 in Miami...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.45,1:10:01.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎收看《新闻观察》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this is Newswatch
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.04,1:10:03.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,由格伦·林克  安·毕肖普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with Glenn Rinker, Ann Bishop,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.20,1:10:05.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,及《新闻观察》获奖制作团队为您呈现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the award-winning Newswatch team.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.72,1:10:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  我是十频道《新闻观察》的格伦·林克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening. I'm Glenn Rinker, Newswatch Ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.36,1:10:12.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密冬季热浪刷新纪录  持续闷热难耐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}While Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heatwave
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.64,1:10:15.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,气温上升到90多华氏度左右\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}bringing temperatures to the mid and upper nineties,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.02,1:10:18.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,而中部和落基山脉覆盖的各州则被大雪覆盖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Central and Rocky Mountain States are buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.37,1:10:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,在科罗拉多州\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In Colorado,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.30,1:10:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不过短短数小时  降雪量就达10英寸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}10 inches of snow has fallen in just a few hours tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.54,1:10:25.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,在落基山脉通行变成几乎不可能的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.04,1:10:28.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,机场关闭  成千上万名旅客滞留\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Airports are shut down, stranding thousands of passengers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.16,1:10:30.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,高速公路被积雪堵住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.32,1:10:32.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,铁轨冻结\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Railroad tracks are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.34,1:10:34.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多州官方告知《新闻观察》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.46,1:10:38.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少已有三人因暴露在寒风中死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at least three have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.26,1:10:40.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,科罗拉多州州长预计将在明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The governor of Colorado is expected tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.62,1:10:42.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,宣布天气紧急状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to declare a weather emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.69,1:10:44.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,国民警卫队可能会被派遣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The National Guard might be called out...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.41,1:10:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,去清空街道和道路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to clear streets and roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.18,1:10:48.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报员预测今夜至明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weather forecasters predict more snow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.52,1:10:50.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,会有更多降雪及强风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and heavy winds tonight and tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.71,1:10:53.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,气温将会降到零华氏度以下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with temperatures dropping well below zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.48,1:10:56.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,佛罗里达南部这里  我们的问题正相反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Back here in south Florida, we've got the opposite problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.80,1:10:59.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,温度和湿度预计会上升\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The heat and humidity are supposed to climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.34,1:11:01.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,本地海滩将人满为患\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Local beaches should be jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.49,1:11:03.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的天气专家沃特·克罗莱斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our weather expert, Walter Cronice...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.72,1:11:06.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍后将在《新闻观察》中带来本地天气预报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will have the local forecast later on Newswatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.10,1:11:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(281.2,209.6)}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}237号房
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.32,1:16:43.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  您拨打的电话无法接通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're sorry. Your call cannot be completed as dialed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.41,1:16:45.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,如需要协助  请打给接线员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you need assistance, please call the operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.23,1:17:03.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.93,1:17:05.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.01,1:17:06.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.99,1:17:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,你找到什么了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.07,1:17:16.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.45,1:17:19.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't see one goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.30,1:17:26.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去的是丹尼说的房间吗  237号房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You went into the room Danny said? To 237?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.87,1:17:28.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.89,1:17:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都没看到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you didn't see anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.06,1:17:32.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.15,1:17:34.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.60,1:17:36.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还在睡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.86,1:17:37.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.83,1:17:46.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定明天早上就会恢复正常了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure he'll be himself again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.45,1:17:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你没找错房间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you sure it was the right room?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.13,1:17:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  或许是丹尼记错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, maybe Danny made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.48,1:17:59.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,他去的肯定是那间房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He must have gone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.93,1:18:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,房门开着  灯也开着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The door was open, the lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.23,1:18:07.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.13,1:18:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,他脖子上的淤伤是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about those bruises on his neck?
