Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.18,1:27:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,这就奇怪了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's strange, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.83,1:27:54.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一点印象都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't have any recollection of that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.36,1:27:59.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,格拉迪先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.70,1:28:03.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经就是这里的管理员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you were the caretaker here.
