Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.42,1:28:17.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.86,1:28:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,才是这里现在的管理员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.04,1:28:25.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是这里的管理员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've always been the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.87,1:28:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.91,1:28:34.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我一直都在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.80,1:28:54.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  托伦斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know, Mr. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.17,1:28:56.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that your son...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.47,1:29:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,正打算带外人进来搅局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is attempting to bring an outside party into this situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.12,1:29:06.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.45,1:29:11.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.10,1:29:14.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,是真的  托伦斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.43,1:29:18.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.86,1:29:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.56,1:29:27.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,黑人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.72,1:29:33.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个黑人厨师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.89,1:29:41.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.47,1:29:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子拥有一种超凡的才能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your son has a very great talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.43,1:29:52.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你还不清楚那究竟有多超凡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you are aware how great it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.62,1:29:56.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他正打算使用这一才能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he is attempting to use that very talent
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.08,1:29:58.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,违背你的意愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}against your will.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.63,1:30:14.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的确是个任性的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is a very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.20,1:30:19.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  托伦斯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Indeed he is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.80,1:30:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个非常任性的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.87,1:30:26.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个非常调皮的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A rather naughty boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.11,1:30:29.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,请恕我大胆直言  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I may be so bold, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.70,1:30:38.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,是因为他的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.54,1:30:43.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,她喜欢胡乱干预\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She interferes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.25,1:30:51.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许该好好跟他们谈谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps they need a good talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.58,1:30:56.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,希望你别介意我这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't mind my saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.20,1:31:00.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许要采取更严厉的手段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.23,1:31:05.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的两个女儿  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My girls, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.55,1:31:09.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,她们一开始毫不关心眺望酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they didn't care for the Overlook at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.18,1:31:14.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个还偷了一盒火柴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of them actually stole a pack of matches
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.54,1:31:16.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,想要放火烧了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and tried to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.12,1:31:21.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我纠正了她们  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I corrected them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.22,1:31:27.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,当我妻子试图阻止我履行职责时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when my wife tried to prevent me from doing my duty,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.52,1:31:31.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也纠正了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I corrected her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.05,1:31:47.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们有雪地车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have the Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.69,1:31:53.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果天气放晴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If the weather breaks,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.42,1:31:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许能开雪地车下山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we might just be able to get down the mountain in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.26,1:32:02.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以先跟护林员打个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could call the forest rangers first
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.32,1:32:06.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then tell them that we're coming
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.29,1:32:12.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们遇到了麻烦  他们还能来找我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that they could start searching for us, in case we didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.44,1:32:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果杰克不肯跟我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if Jack won't come with us,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.12,1:32:24.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,直接告诉他我们自己走就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll just have to tell him that we're going by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.00,1:32:26.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all there is to it.
